Maintainer: Jeremy Coyle <jeremyrcoyle@gmail.com>
Description: tmle3 is a general framework that supports the implementation of a
    range of TMLE parameters with a unified interface. The goal is that the
    tmle3 framework be as general as the mathematical framework upon which it's
    based.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2),
